Package: shinyTimer
Title: Customizable Timer for Shiny Applications
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Maciej", "Banas", email = "banasmaciek@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a customizable timer widget for Shiny applications. Features include countdown and count-up modes, setting different timer formats, pausing and resetting.
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
